reviewText: Amy was simply unique!  I would have loved to meet her in person!  Her personality and singing really touched my emotional zone!

Another example of somebody slapping together a bunch of low rez stock footage to try to make a quick buck. Amy Winehouse was so cool & I really enjoy her interviews but as for this film, it's cheaply made and has no original content. If you are interested in Amy, it's worth watching on Prime but if I had paid for the DVD, I would have felt ripped off.
